songs.lyrics:
Lyrics from Snippet

[Verse 1]
Bitch drinking all this lean, got poured on my wrist
Stupid bitch, you don't get no ween, I just want to hit
Put your bitch twerkin' for the team, baby, we the shit
Make your bitch do it for the 'Gram, everyday we lit (Thanks, Ugly God)

[Chorus]
Yeah, I'm runnin' 'round like Pac-Man, I'm a black man
Call your baby momma up and break the bitch back, man
Now she need a CAT scan and you a mad man (Ayy)
Ugly nigga, new wave, bitch, I'm up like Batman

[Verse 2]
Fresh to death, wipe me down like Mr. Clean (Okay)
Winter fresh (Wassup), I'm in her mouth like Listerine
I ain't never stressed, money long like limousine
Get it off your chest (Okay), we want smoke like nicotine

[Chorus]
Yeah, I'm runnin' 'round like Pac-Man, I'm a black man
Call your baby momma up and break the bitch back, man
Now she need a CAT scan and you a mad man (Ayy)
Ugly nigga, new wave, bitch, I'm up like Batman
